# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:停止#蝕本 嘅意思，即係停止#損失 嘅意思
eng:to stop losses
<eg>
yue:佢已經止蝕咗，唔會再輸錢喇。 (keoi5 jing6 jing6 zik6 sik6 zo2, m4 wui6 zeoi6 syu1 cin4 laa1.)
eng:He has stopped losing money now.

<eg>
yue:公司要止蝕，就要減少支出。 (gung1 siu1 yau5 zik6 sik6, jiu3 yau5 jyun4 jiu6 zit3 ciu3.)
eng:The company needs to stop losses by reducing expenses. [end of text]


